{
  "description": "A nighttime long exposure shot captures a vibrant fireworks display over a city skyline and a bridge. Two prominent bursts of fireworks dominate the upper center of the frame, radiating white, blue, and green light. Below, a long, illuminated bridge stretches across dark water, its lights creating a strong horizontal line.  In the background, a sprawling city skyline is visible, with numerous illuminated buildings and structures. The bridge appears to have multiple spans and unique architectural supports. A second bridge, smaller and more traditional in design, is partially visible to the left. The dark water reflects some of the city lights and fireworks. The overall scene evokes a festive and celebratory atmosphere.",
